That hardly seems like a fair trade.

252
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:15,565
What am I going to do?  

253
00:33:15,600 --> 00:33:18,440
What am I going to do?  
 - It's your call...

254
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:21,400
I guess you can't stay here.

255
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:25,600
Will you take me to Liberty?  

256
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:28,240
You got any money?

257
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:33,320
I've got his rifle...

258
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:38,960
He told me once, it was worth a hundred silver...

259
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,765
Alright, I'll take it.  

260
00:33:44,800 --> 00:33:47,080
