264
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:18,120
Are you implying that you mistrust my judgement, Sheriff?

265
00:34:18,200 --> 00:34:21,240
Well, he did kill two of my scouts so far.

266
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:27,000
Has the thought occurred to you that maybe,  
