300
00:37:17,560 --> 00:37:21,560
Yeah. I need a room for me and...

301
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:25,120
Your wife.

302
00:37:26,680 --> 00:37:28,560
This way.

303
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:39,360
The room is three silver in advance.

304
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:42,760
Half a silver extra for the bath.

305
00:37:43,240 --> 00:37:46,920
Dinner is eight o'clock. One silver each.

306
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:51,365
Take ten.  

307
