308
00:38:33,720 --> 00:38:36,960
I've already seen you.

309
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:57,440
That's why you keep staring at me?

310
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:01,680
Come here.

311
00:39:10,160 --> 00:39:10,925
What for?  

312
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:14,240
