335
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:33,280
I'll take some eggs and coffee.

336
00:42:33,520 --> 00:42:34,925
Just eat your breakfast.  

337
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:35,880
Just eat your breakfast.  
