338
00:42:36,160 --> 00:42:37,800
Already on the road again

339
00:42:37,960 --> 00:42:39,840
Morning.

340
00:42:39,920 --> 00:42:41,800
Where's Matt?

341
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:44,960
Back at his place...  
