00:42:48,200 --> 00:42:50,960
If that be the case, I'm taking you back.

344
00:42:51,200 --> 00:42:54,160
Sorry. She's coming with me.

345
00:42:54,240 --> 00:42:56,120
This ain't your affair, Mister!

346
00:42:56,400 --> 00:42:59,920
Either I take her, or I'll have to draw on you.

347
00:43:01,920 --> 00:43:03,680
I wouldn't.

348
00:43:03,760 --> 00:43:05,640
You got a wife, and a kid on the way.

349
00:43:05,680 --> 00:43:08,880
They need you a lot more than Matt needs her now.

350
00:43:09,560 --> 00:43:10,685
It's suicide boy.  

351
00:43:10,720 --> 00:43:11,800
It's suicide boy.  
 I can't help that!

352
00:43:13,400 --> 00:43:15,280
That's enough, boy!

353
00:43:20,040 --> 00:43:21,920
Let's go.

354
00:43:28,520 --> 00:43:31,280
Not so fast, bigmouth!

355
00:43:43,120 --> 00:43:45,000
LOOK OUT!

356
00:43:56,600 --> 00:44:00,320
Chapter 10:  
 First Blood

