You live the way you do because you want to.

424
00:54:02,480 --> 00:54:06,120
You're afraid to care about anything.

425
00:54:21,160 --> 00:54:24,800
You know... my father didn't have any money...

426
00:54:25,680 --> 00:54:32,000
My mother's parents they had lots of money,  
 but they wouldn't give him any.

427
00:54:33,600 --> 00:54:37,240
So my mama took poison to scare'em...

428
00:54:37,640 --> 00:54:44,000
See, she didn't want to die, but she died anyway.

429
00:54:44,280 --> 00:54:53,360
My father left... I stayed there with my grandparents,  
 until my dad come back to take revenge.

430
00:54:55,320 --> 00:55:00,520
When the shooting stopped, there's just me left.

431
00:55:02,640 --> 00:55:08,400
So I took the guns and the ammo from their bodies,  
 and I went just as far away as I could.

432
00:55:08,600 --> 00:55:11,045
But that's the past!  

433
00:55:11,080 --> 00:55:13,800
But that's the past!  
 We're here together, right now...

434
00:55:13,920 --> 00:55:17,560
Look at me. Look at me!

435
00:55:23,680 --> 00:55:27,165
Do you love me?  

436
00:55:27,200 --> 00:55:29,000
Do you love me?  
 - Yeah.

437
00:55:30,360 --> 00:55:34,000
Then I will not let you ruin our only chance!

438
00:56:05,840 --> 00:56:07,205
There! There he is!  

439
00:56:07,240 --> 00:56:08,560
There! There he is!  
 - Get him!

440
00:56:08,595 --> 00:56:12,200
Fire at will!

441
00:56:32,400 --> 00:56:34,605
Concentrate fire on Saberneck!  

442
00:56:34,640 --> 00:56:37,000
Concentrate fire on Saberneck!  
 - I guess he's not gonna pay now...

443
00:56:46,600 --> 00:56:48,800
Give him cover!

444
00:56:51,280 --> 00:56:53,640
Cover, you guys!

445
00:56:56,600 --> 00:56:59,045
What the hell are you doing man, I thought you'd cover me!  

446
00:56:59,080 --> 00:57:01,040
What the hell are you doing man, I thought you'd cover me!  
