451
00:57:30,240 --> 00:57:31,840
NOW!

452
00:57:36,960 --> 00:57:40,400
I'll get the bike.

453
00:57:51,480 --> 00:57:55,120
Get back! It's not safe

454
00:58:00,160 --> 00:58:03,800
Clayton! Are you still with me?!?

455
00:58:04,320 --> 00:58:05,440
Yeah.

456
00:58:12,240 --> 00:58:15,440
You got'em there!

457
00:58:15,520 --> 00:58:17,040
Matt?

458
00:58:18,800 --> 00:58:22,440
Matt?!? Matthew!

459
00:58:28,360 --> 00:58:32,000
What... What are we gonna do now?

460
00:58:34,400 --> 00:58:38,880
We bury Virgil... If me make it outta here alive.

461
00:58:43,920 --> 00:58:47,640
Chapter 13:  
 Half Past Dead

462
00:58:59,600 --> 00:59:05,440
Just an ordinary man... who's morals wouldn't keep him  
