463
00:59:18,080 --> 00:59:20,365
He's dead alright...  

464
00:59:20,400 --> 00:59:23,520
He's dead alright...  
 Now all I need is that damned Clayton Young.

465
00:59:24,160 --> 00:59:26,005
Send some scouts after them!  

466
00:59:26,040 --> 00:59:29,680
Send some scouts after them!  
 - Yes, Sir. They won't know they're being watched.

467
00:59:33,920 --> 00:59:37,920
Ashes to ashes, you bloody traitor...

468
00:59:38,200 --> 00:59:44,160
Now nothing can stop me...  
 She's all mine.

469
00:59:49,960 --> 00:59:53,960
Like hell she is!

470
00:59:55,600 --> 00:59:57,720
You're nothing but a dog...

471
