I made you a dog of war...

472
01:00:00,680 --> 01:00:04,680
You sat on your land like some stubborn guard dog...

473
01:00:04,760 --> 01:00:08,000
I'll put you down like a dog as well!

474
01:00:13,440 --> 01:00:15,080
Matt!

475
01:00:31,680 --> 01:00:33,645
Where're we going now?  

476
01:00:33,680 --> 01:00:34,960
Where're we going now?  
