477
01:00:35,080 --> 01:00:39,080
To the sands?  
 No one's made it over the mountains!

478
01:00:39,560 --> 01:00:41,365
Without the money, it's gonna be even harder...  

479
01:00:41,400 --> 01:00:43,560
Without the money, it's gonna be even harder...  
