It's true!

483
01:00:53,480 --> 01:00:55,600
You made a deal with the Governor?

484
01:00:55,635 --> 01:00:58,320
You came to kill my husband!

485
01:00:58,400 --> 01:01:00,040
Listen!

486
01:01:01,000 --> 01:01:04,320
I was only gonna get the money we would've gotten anyway -  
 Because YOU killed him, remember?

487
01:01:04,400 --> 01:01:07,240
I didn't mean to kill him!

488
01:01:07,520 --> 01:01:09,160
I loved him!

489
01:01:10,120 --> 01:01:12,280
You have a funny way of showing it!

490
01:01:19,720 --> 01:01:25,720
I was only gonna get the money so we could make the escape...  
 together, you know?

491
01:01:27,640 --> 01:01:30,640
There's a smuggler's hideout in Carpenter Valley.

492
01:01:30,720 --> 01:01:33,480
There's tracks there heading in every direction.

493
01:01:34,000 --> 01:01:35,640
And there's fuel.

494
01:01:40,840 --> 01:01:45,600
I always wanted to head back east... Back to my people.

495
01:01:47,000 --> 01:01:49,800
You'd like their ways!

496
01:01:50,160 --> 01:01:52,720
I don't like nobody's ways but mine.

497
01:01:56,840 --> 01:01:58,480
Let's go.

